attributes.Long form description: The student assembles the furniture. He assembles and screws the first and the second sidebar, then he assembles the base frame, inserts the sidebars into the base frame, and screws them. After, he assembles the first and second brackets of the bottom tray, he inserts the two remaining trays into the sidebars and assembles the first and second brackets of the top and middle trays. Lastly, he screws the four wheels into the base frame.

attributes.Transcription: Hello, thank you for agreeing to take apart in our study.

Your task for now will be to please assemble it.
You may now begin.
First, please take the side pieces, they come in pairs and assemble the side brackets.
